name: Rapunzel (tangled)
description:
Rapunzel (Tangled)

This is the first 3D character model and there are some tips

  1. strength : 0.4~0.8

  2. model : abyssorangemix2 or basilmix

  3. Lots of images that I trained are based on actual movie. Rapunzel always wear dress so if you want to do other clothes, you have to use i2i features.
